data.title: 366 Riola Pl, Pensacola, FL 32506
data.meta_description: Zillow has 11 photos of this $269,900 0.5 Acres lot located at 366 Riola Pl, Pensacola, FL 32506 MLS #634585.
data.text: BOATERS DREAM! Stunning .5-acre waterfront lot near Perdido Key in Pensacola, FL, with 100 feet of Perdido Bay water frontage and an additional 100 feet on deep water access on Bridge Creek. This cleared and graded property is ready for your dream home and includes natural gas hook up and easy access to electric, water, sewer. The lot is situated on a quiet cul-de-sac for privacy and serenity as well as unobstructed views of the Bay! Only 20 minutes from downtown Pensacola, 18 minutes to Johnson Beach, and 33 minutes to Pensacola Beach. End your day with breathtaking sunsets! Don't miss out on this prime waterfront opportunity! https://drive.google.com/file/d/17zfhxLdsD8DJucf920SRiedosTf0pObP/view?ts=642db752
